326
00:21:10,643 --> 00:21:12,801
- That's right! C'mon!
- No!

327
00:21:12,979 --> 00:21:17,059
No! That's not intelligent.
That's not intelligent!

328
00:21:17,150 --> 00:21:20,067
The Honourable Elijah Muhammad
is trying to teach you and I...

329
00:21:20,153 --> 00:21:23,522
...that just as the white man, and any
other man, for that matter, on this earth...

330
00:21:23,614 --> 00:21:26,900
...has the God-given right,
the human right, the civil right...

331
00:21:26,993 --> 00:21:30,278
...the natural right and any other kind
of high rights you can think of...

332
00:21:30,371 --> 00:21:32,494
...to protect himself...

333
00:21:32,582 --> 00:21:35,998
...just as this white man
has the right to defend himself...

334
00:21:36,294 --> 00:21:39,544
...we have the right
to defend ourselves, too.

335
00:21:39,630 --> 00:21:41,132
This is only natural.

336
00:21:41,132 --> 00:21:44,002
This is what The Honourable Elijah
Muhammad is trying to teach you and I.

337
00:21:44,093 --> 00:21:48,672
