339
00:21:53,978 --> 00:21:57,679
..."The Black Muslims: Hate Mongers"...

340
00:21:57,773 --> 00:22:01,723
...would you mind explaining for us
the meaning of yourname...

341
00:22:01,819 --> 00:22:04,489
...which is the letter... X?

342
00:22:04,572 --> 00:22:06,730
Yes, uh, during slavery time...

343
00:22:06,824 --> 00:22:10,442
...the slave master gave the Negro,
so-called Negro...

344
00:22:10,995 --> 00:22:14,993
...uh, named the so-called Negro
