345
00:22:15,082 --> 00:22:17,122
The Honourable Elijah Muhammad
teaches us...

346
00:22:17,210 --> 00:22:20,875
...that once we come into the knowledge
of Islam, the knowledge of ourselves...

347
00:22:20,963 --> 00:22:23,841
...we replace our slave name with an X...

348
00:22:23,841 --> 00:22:27,008
...X in mathematics
representing the unknown.

349
00:22:27,094 --> 00:22:29,134
Since we've been
disconnected or cut off...

350
00:22:29,222 --> 00:22:33,266
...from our own history, our own past,
our own culture, our own land...

351
00:22:33,351 --> 00:22:37,218
...we use the X, the unknown,
until we get back to our country.

352
00:22:37,313 --> 00:22:40,647
I see. Thank you. Er, Dr Payson?

353
00:22:40,983 --> 00:22:43,688
Mr X is a... He's a demagogue.

