00:22:43,778 --> 00:22:46,695
He has no place to go, so he exaggerates.

355
00:22:46,781 --> 00:22:49,402
He's a disservice
to every good, law-abiding...

356
00:22:49,492 --> 00:22:51,983
...churchgoing American Negro
