359
00:23:01,587 --> 00:23:06,380
Well, for the white man
to ask the black man...

360
00:23:06,551 --> 00:23:08,627
...why he hates him...

361
00:23:08,886 --> 00:23:11,347
...is like the wolf asking the sheep...

362
00:23:11,347 --> 00:23:14,134
...or the rapist asking the raped:
