418
00:26:09,901 --> 00:26:12,111
...and I just... I wanted to ask you...

419
00:26:12,111 --> 00:26:15,278
...what can a white person like myself
who isn't prejudiced...

420
00:26:15,364 --> 00:26:18,864
...what can I do to help you
