00:44:05,017 --> 00:44:07,687
I just got a lot of work to do, that's all.

701
00:44:11,774 --> 00:44:15,902
- How can you work?
- Well, because we have to teach.

702
00:44:15,987 --> 00:44:20,696
We got to teach the people, we got to
teach on Solomon and Moses, David...

703
00:44:20,783 --> 00:44:22,990
Solomon had 700 wives.

704
00:44:23,077 --> 00:44:26,576
A man's good deeds,
they far outweigh any of his...

705
00:44:26,664 --> 00:44:30,578
(chuckles)
My father used to say that, uh...

706
00:44:30,668 --> 00:44:33,752
...you can't make a rooster stop crowing
once the sun has come up.

707
00:44:33,838 --> 00:44:36,293
Well, the sun is up.

708
00:44:36,716 --> 00:44:40,298
* I know that lucky old sun

709
00:44:42,972 --> 00:44:45,012
* Has nothin' to do

710
00:44:49,770 --> 00:44:52,558
* But roll around heaven all day

711
00:44:55,651 --> 00:44:57,858
- * Oh...
- * Dear Lord... *

712
00:44:57,945 --> 00:45:00,780
So what do I say
about this national day of mourning...

713
00:45:00,865 --> 00:45:03,237
...so-called national day of mourning?

714
00:45:03,326 --> 00:45:05,614
I say the white man's acts of violence
should be condemned...

715
00:45:05,703 --> 00:45:07,945
...not only by our beliefs, but by his own.

716
00:45:09,165 --> 00:45:12,000
The holy Koran teaches us
that those who work evil...

717
00:45:12,084 --> 00:45:16,996
...will be condemned, or punished,
or judged, according to their works.

718
00:45:17,089 --> 00:45:22,084
The holy Bible teaches us that you reap
what you sow. This is divine justice.

719
00:45:22,178 --> 00:45:26,092
In the soil of the Americas, the white man
has planted the seeds of hatred.

720
00:45:26,182 --> 00:45:28,174
He's planted the seeds of violence.

721
00:45:28,267 --> 00:45:30,474
He's allowed those weeds to grow up...

722
00:45:30,561 --> 00:45:34,179
...and choke the lives out of millions
of black men and women for 400 years.

723
00:45:34,273 --> 00:45:38,852
In fact, the lives of Indians
in these Americas for the last 500 years.

724
00:45:38,945 --> 00:45:40,569
And now those same weeds...

725
00:45:40,655 --> 00:45:43,691
...have choked one of his own gardeners,
in fact, his chief gardener...

726
00:45:43,783 --> 00:45:47,152
...and you ask me what I say.
I only say what the Bible says.

727
00:45:47,245 --> 00:45:49,949
I say what the Koran says.

728
00:45:50,456 --> 00:45:52,698
I say it's justice.

729
00:45:52,792 --> 00:45:54,831
- (cheering and applause)
- As salaam alaikum.

730
00:45:54,919 --> 00:45:56,793
(crowd shouts)

731
00:45:56,879 --> 00:45:59,880
Minister X, don't you even feel
a little bit of remorse...

732
00:45:59,966 --> 00:46:02,587
...saddened by
President Kennedy's assassination?

733
00:46:02,677 --> 00:46:05,761
Sir, I don't think
anybody here would deny...

734
00:46:05,847 --> 00:46:07,886
...that when you send your chickens out
in the morning from your barnyard...

735
00:46:07,974 --> 00:46:11,473
...the chickens will return that evening
to your barnyard, not your neighbour's.

736
00:46:11,561 --> 00:46:15,143
This is a prime example of the devil's
chickens coming back home to roost.

737
00:46:15,231 --> 00:46:17,150
That the chickens that he's sent out...

738
00:46:17,150 --> 00:46:19,226
...the violence he's perpetrated
here and abroad...

739
00:46:19,318 --> 00:46:20,694
...be it four children in Birmingham...

740
00:46:20,778 --> 00:46:22,818
...or Medgar Evers,
or Lumumba overin Africa.

741
00:46:22,905 --> 00:46:25,231
I think this same violence
has come back to claim one of their own.

742
00:46:25,324 --> 00:46:26,867
Now, being an old farm boy myself...

743
00:46:26,951 --> 00:46:29,193
...chickens coming home to roost
nevermade me sad.

744
00:46:29,287 --> 00:46:32,905
- In fact, it's only made me glad.
- (reporters shout)

745
00:46:32,999 --> 00:46:35,953
(coughs)

746
00:46:36,043 --> 00:46:39,128
(sniffs and gasps)

747
00:46:40,715 --> 00:46:42,754
Did you...

748
00:46:42,842 --> 00:46:45,131
...read the paper today?

749
00:46:48,264 --> 00:46:50,387
Yes, sir, I did.

750
00:46:53,144 --> 00:46:54,768
That...

751
00:46:54,854 --> 00:46:57,808
...was a bad statement you made.

752
00:47:00,359 --> 00:47:04,025
You knew from my instructions...

753
00:47:04,113 --> 00:47:09,238
...no Minister was to make
any statements against this man.

754
00:47:09,327 --> 00:47:11,865
The country loved this man.

755
00:47:12,288 --> 00:47:14,446
You have made it...

756
00:47:14,540 --> 00:47:17,411
...hard for Muslims...

757
00:47:18,377 --> 00:47:20,335
...(coughs) in general.

758
00:47:20,421 --> 00:47:22,414
(coughs)

759
00:47:22,507 --> 00:47:24,546
Yes, sir.

760
00:47:24,634 --> 00:47:30,886
We must dissociate ourselves
from your terrible blunder.

761
00:47:33,768 --> 00:47:36,010
I must silence you.

762
00:47:36,687 --> 00:47:38,929
For 90 days...

763
00:47:39,607 --> 00:47:45,728
...you must not make
any statements to the press...

764
00:47:46,531 --> 00:47:50,943
...nor are you to speak at any temples.

765
00:47:52,203 --> 00:47:54,242
Yes, sir.

766
00:47:54,914 --> 00:47:57,868
Yes, sir. I submit 100 per cent.

767
00:48:05,174 --> 00:48:08,045
(phlegmy cough)

768
00:48:08,136 --> 00:48:12,133
(coughs painfully)

769
00:48:20,273 --> 00:48:22,396
(coughing continues)

770
00:48:27,280 --> 00:48:31,942
(laboured coughing)

771
00:48:37,206 --> 00:48:39,282
(telephone rings)

772
00:48:39,375 --> 00:48:42,874
(child babbles happily)

773
00:48:55,308 --> 00:48:57,384
You leave us alone.

774
00:48:58,394 --> 00:49:00,850
- Betty?
- Leave us alone. Stop calling here.

775
00:49:00,938 --> 00:49:04,853
Who's putting you up to this?
We have children here!

776
00:49:04,942 --> 00:49:07,184
Stop it! Stop...

777
00:49:07,945 --> 00:49:09,985
Hello?

778
00:49:18,831 --> 00:49:22,746
- (whispers) It's all right. It's OK.
- They keep calling.

779
00:49:23,544 --> 00:49:26,166
- They keep calling...
- Shhhh.

780
00:49:27,089 --> 00:49:29,759
(whispers) Shh. Now, just, uh...

781
00:49:30,927 --> 00:49:33,678
We'll take the babies, put them into bed.

782
00:49:33,763 --> 00:49:35,886
C'mon, babies, let's go to bed now.

783
00:49:35,973 --> 00:49:38,891
- C'mon. Come on.
- Bedtime.

784
00:49:38,976 --> 00:49:41,016
Let's go.

785
00:49:41,103 --> 00:49:44,804
- Good night, Mommy, good night, Daddy.
- There you go. Night-night.

786
00:49:44,899 --> 00:49:47,022
- Good night, Sidney.
- Night-night!

787
00:49:47,109 --> 00:49:50,276
- Come on.
- Good night.

788
00:50:00,456 --> 00:50:03,540
Brother Minister, I have to level with you.

789
00:50:04,001 --> 00:50:07,750
They gave me a mission.
But I couldn't do it.

790
00:50:08,172 --> 00:50:11,375
- I love y'all.
- What kind of mission?

791
00:50:14,220 --> 00:50:16,343
To wire your car...

792
00:50:16,430 --> 00:50:20,475
...so it would explode
when you turned the ignition.

793
00:50:21,853 --> 00:50:27,191
The ministers say you're spreading
untruths about Mr Muhammad.

794
00:50:27,275 --> 00:50:31,687
The ministers say that you are
the greatest hypocrite, a... a Judas.

795
00:50:32,029 --> 00:50:34,318
A Benedict Arnold.

796
00:50:34,407 --> 00:50:39,235
The ministers say that
your tongue should be cut out...

797
00:50:39,620 --> 00:50:42,787
...and delivered
to Mr Muhammad's doorstep.

798
00:50:43,541 --> 00:50:47,159
- And what do you say?
- I'm with you, Brother Minister.

799
00:50:47,503 --> 00:50:51,086
- You'll be marked for death.
- Yes, sir.

800
00:50:51,174 --> 00:50:52,716
Let me die, then.

801
00:51:01,642 --> 00:51:03,849
(sighs)

802
00:51:04,604 --> 00:51:08,436
Brother, I can't come between you
and your father.

803
00:51:08,900 --> 00:51:12,849
- You're my father.
- Brother, go on home.

804
00:51:13,404 --> 00:51:16,239
Don't come back. That's an order.

805
00:51:23,039 --> 00:51:25,162
Yes, sir.


